- **Crypto products are unregulated and highly risky.** There may be no regulatory recourse for losses.
- This tool is for **educational and personal use only**. Test with sandbox mode first.
- Always use **Sandbox/Paper Trading** mode before risking real capital.
- Never share your API keys or secret keys with anyone.
- This is not financial advice. Trade at your own risk.

---

## Security

- API keys are entered client-side and never stored permanently
- All API communication uses HTTPS
- Request signing uses HMAC-SHA256 (Legacy) or Ed25519 (CSX) as per CoinSwitch specs
- Enable Sandbox mode for safe testing

---

## Tech Stack

- **Python 3.9+**
- **Streamlit** — UI framework
- **Plotly** — Interactive charts
- **Pandas** — Data manipulation
- **Requests** — HTTP client
- **ed25519** / **cryptography** — Request signing

